  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the different response of Ursodeoxycholic Acid in primary biliary
      cholangitis only and primary biliary cholangitis with high immune globulin G or
      aminotransferase at West China Hospital from 2008-2017.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
